trans-unit.source: Represents the position of the iterator to the next node in the intersection of two sets of nodes.
trans-unit.target: Representa a posição do iterator para o próximo nó na intersecção de dois conjuntos de nós.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current result navigator.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o navegador de resultado atual.

trans-unit.source: The Current property gets modified when the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A> method sets the Current property to the next node and returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; otherwise, the Current property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade atual obtém modificada quando o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A>método define a propriedade atual para o próximo nó e devolve <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; caso contrário, a propriedade atual permanece inalterada.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator to the next node in the union.
trans-unit.target: Positions iterator para o próximo nó na União.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if there are no more nodes.
Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if this function initializes the right nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Devolve <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>se esta função inicializa o direito iterator aninhado.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the left-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Devolve <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>se o nó seguinte tem de ser recuperados do iterator esquerda-nested.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the right-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Devolve <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>se o nó seguinte tem de ser recuperados do iterator direito-nested.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the iterator's <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A> property is set to the next node in the iteration.
trans-unit.target: Devolve <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>se o iterator <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A>propriedade está definida para o próximo nó da iteração.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>
